        public static List<String> splitSignature(String sig)
        Split the signature string using the same algorithm as in method 'Annotation makeSignature(CstString signature)' in dx (dx/src/com/android/dx/dex/file/AnnotationUtils.java) Rules are: "" - scan to ';' or '<'. Consume ';' but not '<'. - scan to 'L' without consuming it. ""
